#### zero-inflation





::: {#tbl-zeroinf-poisson .cell tbl-cap='Zero-inflated poisson model'}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(glmmTMB)
zinf_fit1 = glmmTMB(
  family = "poisson",
  data  = needles,
  formula = shared_syr ~ age + sex + homeless*polydrug,
  ziformula = ~ age + sex + homeless + polydrug # fit won't converge with interaction
)

zinf_fit1 |> 
  parameters(exponentiate = TRUE) |> 
  print_md()
```

::: {.cell-output-display}


